description: This Chainlink VRF common Gaston purrs with a rating of 1, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 3, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, 3 for East, 1 for South, and 1 for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/60013-43110-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [3 Votes, Common]
